But that does n't mean all Olivia 's relationships are secure . How will Olivia react when she learns what peppy underling Quinn has been hiding ? `` A lot of that depends on who she is , '' said Washington . `` I do n't think Olivia makes decisions on how to treat people or how to navigate a situation blindly . She really takes into account the circumstance at hand . ''

